#### Overview

This port of lwIP 1.3.0 combines 
- the lwIP base package v1.3.0
- the unix port from lwIP's contrib package v1.3.0
- our own bottom ('device driver') interface

The last two are split between two patch files

Sources and more information:
http://savannah.nongnu.org/projects/lwip/
http://www.sics.se/~adam/lwip/

#### Variants

We have the following variants of the lwip patches:
- nexus	:		nexus specific locking + zerocopy transfer on rx
- nexus.nofastdev:	nexus-specific locking, NO zerocopy transfer on rx 
- nexus.nosys:		unix pthread locking + zerocopy ...

UPDATE 2012-12-22: only nexus.nofastdev supports the new NXCONFIG_DEVICE_BLIND options

